name: Factory Tycoon
blurb: A strategy game where you build, automate and optimize your own manufacturing plant.  Machines, workers, automation and assemblies!

rewards.reward: - Simple \r\n- 1 Copy of the game, nothing more, nothing less.
Early bird! A signed T-shirt, an exclusive, large format poster, and two copies of the game.  Hurry before it's gone!
- Team - Want to play with a friend?  Get an additional copy for someone of your choosing.\r\n2 Copies of the game in total.
- Pinup - 1 Exclusive, large format game poster, which will never be re-printed.\r\n1 Copy of the game.
- Wear it Out - 1 T-Shirt, signed by us!\r\n1 Exclusive, large format, game poster.\r\n1 Copy of the game.

- Almost Famous - 
Listing in the official game credits, with any bogus "title" of your choice.  Titles must be between 5 and 20 characters long, including spaces, and can not be offensive in any way.  The color of titles can also be chosen.  Example: Joe Robinson - Llama Herder.  Of course, you will be able to enter your friend's names instead. ;D  If the same name is entered more than once, it will be included in the list multiple times.
1 Exclusive, large format, game poster.
2 Copies of the game.

- Famous - Your name, immortalized in the game in some way (machine, manufactured part, etc. named after you) Example: Name>Bill Kelly - Machine>Bilk-EEly-307.

Listing in the official game credits, with any bogus "title" of your choice.  Titles must be between 5 and 20 characters long, including spaces, and can not be offensive in any way.  The color of titles can also be chosen.  Example: Joe Robinson - Llama Herder.  Of course, you will be able to enter your friend's names instead. ;D  If the same name is entered more than once, it will be included in the list multiple times.
1 Exclusive, large format, game poster.
3 Copies of the game.

- +1 Back Scratcher - Invite to a Dungeons & Dragons game day with the development team.  Warning! Expect tough, custom, old-school game rules. Game will take place in Ottawa, Ontario, Canada. Travel & associated costs are not included.
Listing in the game's official credits (like in the "almost famous" reward).
1 exclusive, large format game poster. 
3 copies of the game.

- Artist - Draw literally anything on a single piece of 8.5" by 11" paper, in any way you choose, and mail it to us.  We will attempt to model some piece of the game after it. When we are done, we will draw in the changes we've made (Remember we are programmers, not artists) and send the paper back to you.  Includes listing in the game's official credits (like in the "almost famous" reward), an exclusive, large format game poster, and three copies of the game.

- Obsession -
Kent and David will BOTH fly to wherever you live, within Canada or the US, and hang out for a day. We will participate in (almost) any activity(s) of your choice.  Shared status with the creators in the game's official credits.
The awesome piece of every limited quantity reward (including additional supply if required).
Two game posters, one signed by David, the other by Kent. This reward is the only way to ever get a signed version of the limited-edition poster.
10 copies of the game for friends of your choosing.
We will only fly to Canada or the US, you may choose to meet us anywhere in Canada or the US though.
